Cell["\<\
Note : - To generate phase diagrams for different parameters, the system \
parameters can be changed. The Kerr nonlinearity can be set to zero to obtain \
the plot for a standard optomechanical system without additional \
non-linearity. The parameters used here are the same as Figure 2 of the \
paper. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.9555937590409327`*^9, {3.9559650280671997`*^9, 3.955965063322688*^9}, {
